✔ PROBLEMS :

✔ String problems
Reverse string
Remove duplicates
Implement strstr
Palindrome checks

✔ Pointer problems
Swap using pointers
Matrix operations
Array of pointers

✔ Bit manipulation problems
Count set bits
Reverse bits
Detect power of 2
Find missing/duplicate number

✔ Memory simulation
Implement malloc/free (simple model)

✔ Audio-specific problems ⭐⭐⭐
Circular/ring buffer implementation (MUST KNOW)
Audio buffer queue management
Sample format conversion (int16 to float)
Endian conversion for audio data
Multi-channel audio interleaving/de-interleaving
